commentary: Meth to McCullum, OUT fifth time lucky for Zimbabwe! After letting off McCullum for four times, Sibanda holds a stunner at backward point by leaping to his left and getting hold of the ball with both his hands. The stint at NSW seems to have rubbed the Aussie superstitions on McCullum as he is dismissed for 87
